<p>Add users and specify their roles. Each must log in with their unique credentials. You can add users, specify their roles and control their permissions</p>

<p class="lead">Create users</p>

<ul>
	<li>Sign in to the&nbsp;web portal</li>
	<li>Click on ‘retail’ and ‘user management’ and select ‘users’&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Click ‘+’ to add a new user and provide the required information</li>
	<li>Select desired role and assign to user</li>
</ul>

<p class="lead">Create roles</p>

<ul>
	<li>Go to the web portal</li>
	<li>Click on retail then user management and select roles</li>
	<li>Click ‘+’ to add a new role&nbsp;and provide the required information</li>
	<li>Select the desired permissions and save</li>
